---
title: "Parties & Events - PD Thai Cuisine"
description: "Planning a party or group event near UT Austin? Submit an inquiry with PD Thai Cuisine and we'll help you plan a table that fits."
---
{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
<section class="bg-[#fdfaf5] py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-7">
    <div class="mb-14 text-center" data-reveal="up">
      <p class="mb-2.5 text-[13px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-primary-600">{{ client.parties.kicker }}</p>
      <h1 class="text-balance mb-6 text-[32px] font-bold tracking-tight text-[#241b16] sm:text-[40px]">{{ client.parties.heading }}</h1>
      <p class="text-[16.5px] leading-relaxed text-[#4a3d34]">{{ client.parties.paragraphOne }}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#ece2d3] bg-white p-7 sm:p-10" data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay="1">
      <p class="mb-6 text-center text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[#4a3d34]">{{ client.parties.formNote }}</p>
      <iframe src="{{ client.parties.formUrl }}" frameborder="0" width="100%" height="565" scrolling="no"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
